                </details>
            </div>

            <div class="summary-section">
                <h2>üéØ Key Takeaways</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>MySQL can be installed on Windows, Mac, and Linux</li>
                    <li>Always secure your installation with a strong root password</li>
                    <li>MySQL Workbench provides a visual interface for database management</li>
                    <li>Test your installation by connecting and creating a database</li>
                    <li>Keep your root password safe and secure</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

